[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    523[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   "trend_description": "Mortality risk has increased from 0.18 to 0.34 over the last 12 hours",
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    524[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   "top_factors": [
